;搾乳エナジードレインであなたの霊力を5000以上にする
@MILESTONE_CHECK_822

SIF MAXBASE:0:霊力 >= 5000
	RETURN 1


;＜小型霊力抽出装置＞・＜家庭用魔力貯蔵器＞入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_822

ITEM:小型霊力抽出装置 += 1
ITEM:家庭用魔力貯蔵器 += 1
PRINTL Using Energy Drain, you really where able to take energy from Ningen.
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","...I see! Really? Wow! This is very interesting!"
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","I'd like to see if I can use it! Can I take a blood sample!?"
PRINTL
PRINTLC [ 0] Sure
PRINTLC [ 1] I'm scared of injections
INPUT
SIF RESULT
	CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","You're an adult, you can handle it..."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","......... Okay, thanks! I smell some innovation here...!"
PRINTL
PRINTW ～Later～
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","So, through analysis and application, I managed to create a ＜Portable Spirit Energy Extractor＞."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","If I use this to milk your slave, it should be able to steal her spirit energy just like your energy drain!"
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","And as a side effect, if the slave has mana, then it will be drained as well."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","Don't forget to check the ＜Domestic Mana Reservoir＞, to confirm if the mana is drained properly."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","Everything you drain will be automatically seperated and stored, so please try to save up a lot."
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained ＜Portable Spirit Energy Extractor＞.","水色"
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained ＜Domestic Mana Reservoir＞.","水色"
PRINTL During training, you can attach the【Portable Spirit Energy Extractor】to a【Lactating】Slave,
PRINTL allowing it to extract and store spirit energy and mana.
CALL MAGIC_STORAGE



;＜小型霊力抽出装置＞で霊力を貯蔵する
@MILESTONE_CHECK_823

SIF MONEY:貯蔵霊力
	RETURN 1


;＜霊力抽出装置＞入手・スケジュール【抽出】解放・システム【抽出魔力での経費削減】解放
@MILESTONE_REWARD_823

ITEM:霊力抽出装置 += 1
PRINTL You managed to extract some spirit energy by using the  ＜Portable Spirit Energy Extractor＞.
PRINTL When reporting to Eugene, he excitedly begins writing a report, thanks you, and leaves.
PRINTL
PRINTW ～Later～
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","So, the large-scale ＜Spirit Energy Extractor＞ was built."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"あなた","＞Great."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","With this guy, you can extract spirit energy just by throwing slaves in and leaving them alone!"
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","...well, the mana consumption is much more intense."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","Because of that, if you attach this part to the reservoir, you'll be able to use stored mana."
CALL RESIDENT_KOJO,@"ユジン","You can turn it on and off, so use it however you want."
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained ＜Spirit Energy Extractor＞.","水色"
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【Schedule】→【Extraction】enabled.","水色"
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【Cost reduction with extracted mana】enabled","水色"
PRINTL 【Management】→【Use Mana Batteries To Reduce Costs】to turn it on or off.



